<title>USA: Informix sues Oracle over hiring.</title>
<headline>Informix sues Oracle over hiring.</headline>
<dateline>MENLO PARK, Calif. 1997-01-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>Informix Software Inc said on Friday it has filed suit against Oracle Corp over the potential theft of trade secrets after Oracle hired away 11 Informix employees.</p>
<p>The suit filed in Portland, Ore., accuses Oracle and former Informix executive Gary Kelley of misappropriation of trade secrets and unfair competition, and seeks injunctive relief and punitive damages.</p>
<p>Informix said it acted after Oracle's recent hiring of 11 employees from the Informix product development laboratory in Portland.</p>
